tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE AR_Session_Data (
    session_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id UUID,
    session_date DATE,
    session_duration INTERVAL,
    session_data JSONB
)

CREATE TABLE ar_session_data (
  session_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  user_id INT,
  session_date TIMESTAMP,
  duration_minutes INT
)

CREATE TABLE user_feedback (
  feedback_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  session_id INT,
  feedback_rating INT,
  feedback_text TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE session_events (
  event_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  session_id INT,
  event_type VARCHAR(50),
  event_timestamp TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE AR_Sessions (
  session_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  user_id INT,
  session_start TIMESTAMP,
  session_end TIMESTAMP,
  session_duration INTERVAL,
  session_data JSONB
)

CREATE TABLE AR_Events (
  event_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  session_id INT,
  event_type VARCHAR(50),
  event_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
  event_data JSONB
)

CREATE TABLE AR_Errors (
  error_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  event_id INT,
  error_message TEXT,
  error_timestamp TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE AR_Analytics (
  analytics_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  session_id INT,
  total_events INT,
  total_errors INT,
  average_session_duration INTERVAL
)

CREATE TABLE ar_session_data (
    session_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id UUID,
    session_date DATE,
    session_duration INTERVAL,
    session_events JSONB
);
